text: AMD received a favorable analyst note today. Falling inflation fueled a risk-on mentality on Tuesday.

title: AMD: Promising Upside By 2025
text: Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.'s Q3 results and guidance initially disappointed the market, but the stock has rallied to multi-month highs. The launch of AI chips could drive the stock to all-time highs, with projected AI revenue exceeding $2 billion in 2024 alone. The stock trades at a base case of only 20x '25 EPS targets, but AI GPU chip sales could provide a substantial boost to conservative targets.
